+# Changelog
+
+## 1.0.0 - 2026-04-13
+
+- Initial release.
+- Overrides `speckit.clarify` to use Claude Code's `AskUserQuestion` picker instead of Markdown-table rendering.
+- Overrides `speckit.checklist` to use `AskUserQuestion` for the Option / Candidate / Why It Matters selection.
